page.title: 04SUPERNATURAL
page.content: {Lumb Mill-reported by Mrs S Beaumont About 100 years ago a woman jumped from the loft window killing herself. She is believed to walk around the mill, now a private house, once a year. The electric cooker occasionally turns itself off and on and the timer bell goes off on its own. {Lower Shaw Booth-reported by Mr S Cann In the 1600s the house was owned by a privateer. He brought home a black slave who was converted to christianity but when he died he was refused burial by the church and was buried in the barn by the house which he is said to haunt. {UFO sighting-reported by Mrs F Marsden About 7 years ago Mrs Marsden saw a cigar-shaped object in the sky above the moor by Castle Carr Road. It was orange and remained stationary. It was visible for 10 minutes.
